column4: Text
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "6F34115840478950F50FD59DF9637A04", "This must be it! No matter how I look at it, it looks a plain meteorite.")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "AEE937064B8BA54C4B1CFD85CF027A7F", "We looked at it, and we can\'t tell anything. Let\'s crack it!")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "3D29A2F04384D2ABA17A12A1F3AD64EC", "Whadda ya think you\'re doing? You reckless clod!")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "7F558B944D27CBBF018084894F17B955", "Looks like a plain old meteorite to me.")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "14F180F648FF5608779E81BDF5570A0B", "Sorry to look so plain and old.")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "5B4CEEB84BE190A36A563389A01CB9C1", "Wow!")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "081A6E4D478A0BB8A74B14860A14D0AD", "You\'re a Digimon?! Who are you?")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "13694E774C8582B2B3908EAD8BB9F173", "My name is Meteormon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "88A4E4BD438A705074273D821EED8573", "Do you know about the island\'s danger?")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "C98B744A46F0B186176CDDAA06FFB336", "I know nothing!")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "A5BA6C8546A2CCC6EF6B83BFB6BAD806", "You know nothing?! You sure you\'re not hiding something?")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "0476450E430B6C69C1E7A681B9E46801", "How rude! Alright! Why don\'t we battle to prove who is right!")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "431690D145B1301701904B986E114324", "Alright! Let\'s go for it.")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "E15472C44D6906DE675AEA937645ECA2", "I give up. You\'re so strong.")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "76C87E2842B95F6DD8AA9E8DF7AF6486", "Whatever you know, tell me about the island\'s danger.")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "A8D388BB4BA646A4B918C59CE8FEAC3D", "I was just born, so I don\'t know anything!")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "63C1B54649FBBF1520AD03B9BB5D9265", "The Meteorite Tribe is born in the sky and then falls to the ground.")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "FBB1D9B843542BB52751B1AD03A4B34B", "Then we sleep for a long time. Actually, I was supposed to sleep much longer, but...")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "5A23A4844C2B92419E2934B008D33156", "Time goes much faster here.")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "DACF4CCA404DEC52D7420E9CAF8518E3", "Probably. Anyway, I\'ll go check out the island.")
NSLOCTEXT("[4D0C6B4543DAADCBB7B19EAB5465E560]", "1E0E9CF742999F7942738483FF7FE1C6", "We couldn\'t find any clues. Let\'s get out fast.")
